 field with that generated by\nthe magnetorotational instability operating in the accretion disc. Longer\noutbursts (a few days) could result from the disc instability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Mar 2017 07:43:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-28"}
